===============================================================================
ATTRIBUTION & CITATION
===============================================================================

When using the schema/tools in code: retain the MIT copyright & permission text
in your distribution.

When using or adapting catalog entries or documentation:
- Provide attribution: “Impossibility Patterns Finder (IPF) — Catalog v1.0”
- Include DOI link(s) below
- Indicate changes, if any

Project citation:
Williams, Thomas C. 2025. "Impossibility Patterns Finder (IPF) Schema and Catalog v1.0." Zenodo. 
https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.17393656

For individual catalog entries, cite as:
Williams, Thomas C. 2025. "IPF-XXXXX: [Entry Title]." In Impossibility Patterns Finder Catalog v1.0. Zenodo.
https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.17393656

